content.rendered:
Directed by Revathi

Written by Sameer Arora. Kausar Munir

Cast Aamir Khan. Kajol (Sujata). Aahana Kumra (Sanjana). Priyamani (Nanda). Prakash Raj. Riddhi Kumar (Sharda). Maala Parvathi. Rahul Bose. Rajeev Khandelwal. Kamal Sadanah. Vaibhav Gohil (Friend). Vishal Jethwa (Venkatesh). Anant Mahadevan(Guruji). Vishal Meena Phagi. Aneet Padda (Nandini). Ebadat Akram Dunia (Villain). Jaineeraj Rajpurohit (Mohan). Lovely Bhati. Geeta Sodhi (Bhawani)

Languages Hindi

Producers Shraddha Agrawal. Priyank Jain. Varsha Kukreja. Aftab Qureshi. Yogiraj Shetty. Anshuman Singh. Suraj Singh. Yogesh Tevatia.

Production Blive Productions. RTake Studios.
